OL,3,CWarmest day of year in Northern
OL,4,CIreland on Bank Holiday Monday
OL,6,FArmagh recorded the highest
OL,7,Ftemperature in Northern Ireland on
OL,8,FBank Holiday Monday.
OL,10,FThe Met Office said a temperature of
OL,11,F26.3C was recorded, marking the
OL,12,Fwarmest day of 2026 so far.
OL,14,FHillsborough, Co Down logged 25.6C,
OL,15,Fwhile following close behind was
OL,16,FDerrylin, Co Fermanagh at 25.5C.
OL,26,@sD@EOXvD@bOXxD@_OX
