OL,3,CWarmest day of year in Northern
OL,4,CIreland on Bank Holiday Monday
OL,6,FPeople flocked to beaches and beauty
OL,7,Fspots to soak up the best of the hot
OL,8,Fweather including at Helen's Bay, Co
OL,9,FDown which recorded a temperature of
OL,10,F25.1C.
OL,12,FThe highest reading taken in
OL,13,FCastlederg, Co Tyrone was 25C.
OL,15,FThe UK recorded its all-time hottest
OL,16,FMay temperature as a part of London
OL,17,Fhit 33.5C.
OL,19,FThe Met Office said the high was at
OL,20,FHeathrow, in the west of the capital,
OL,21,Fshortly after 1pm.
